					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13730896#post-4775541</guid>
				<title>A belated author post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13730896/scp-4291#post-4775541</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 15 Sep 2020 20:02:38 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Riemann</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1787775</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>A hearty thank you to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cybersqyd" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5336470&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600200157" alt="cybersqyd" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5336470)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cybersqyd" >cybersqyd</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ocuin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6104981&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600200157" alt="OCuin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6104981)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ocuin" >OCuin</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4558017&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600200157" alt="Grigori Karpin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4558017)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" >Grigori Karpin</a></span> for their help on this one.</p> <p>The idea came to me shortly after reading <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5612">SCP-5612</a>, and I thought - can I trick someone into reading a ~500 word dick joke? Anyways, here's an article that's full of increasingly obvious references to the fact that this was only ever a dick joke. Cheers!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
